{"tid":1123834,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「彪析」今晚曼聯贏波／和波都唔出奇","createTime":"2019-04-24T16:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T02:14:10.000Z","uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14550cb3f3e14d2649ac8e7a85ac7dc0683d75ba","tid":1123834,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"曼聯近績係差，但球員本身既個人能力唔係廢 <br />\n主要係心態問題，正如當時一轉領隊成班即升晒Grade <br />\n但果陣對PSG 奇蹟反勝後，就Gel 到上天花板，飄飄然既感覺令一眾球員沉淪當中<br />\n及後對壘阿仙奴、狼隊，其輕敵招致落敗<br />\n&quot; 一子錯滿盤皆落索 &quot;<br />\n輸俾巴塞出局後，歐聯夢碎<br />\n一眾大帝心理狀態、戰意跌至谷底 <br />\n甚至被愛華頓羞辱至 4：0 慘敗 <br />\n<br />\n但係要留意，班大帝近績咁差<br />\n主要係輸心態 <br />\n特別係普巴呢種人，EQ真係唔高得去邊 <br />\n<br />\n而上場被愛華頓羞辱 4：0 可視為 Wake up call <br />\n有助提升今場大戰既士氣，令曼聯浴火重生<br />\n要記住：「一個人衰到貼地，受到極大刺激後，的確有機會咸魚翻生」<br />\n<br />\n班大帝今場突然上心極力阻擋曼城奪冠 <br />\n真心唔奇<br />\n班球員最鍾意就係駁嘴，係有事實根據<br />\n當年，摩連奴嘲諷講左句：「曼聯入到前四係奇蹟」 <br />\n當大家都睇淡曼聯，覺得絕望既時候 <br />\n班大帝就偏偏上晒心咁瘋狂贏波，後來居上<br />\n（p.s. 當時蘇帥岩岩入主，根本未有時間教到D咩，純綷係班大帝想駁摩連奴嘴）<br />\n <br />\n另外蘇斯克查再唔反底，你估佢個位又坐得穩咩？ <br />\n戰術部署一定同卡域克拍住上做到好足 <br />\n加上今仗曼聯主場出擊<br />\n不得不提2月尾 曼聯主場 vs 利物浦，賽果係 0: 0 <br />\n唔好以為走出奧脫福個門口係容易既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11d71cc672e9bdaa0e2a20333a8655ca50bfe66","tid":1123834,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"收嘴啦"},{"pid":"e980075a2d6e3036786767fc0cf6e32ab4f7d6c7","tid":1123834,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"本來仲有機會，你出完post就無喇"},{"pid":"d9a824e032aee749779a4b2b67a3125f0fb81644","tid":1123834,"uid":99827,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"曼聯仲有5%機會,而家5%都沒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2239f51a13e1ab919dc0a99e99addf27a67e62","tid":1123834,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"無可能 根本唔關鬥心事<br />\n<br />\n上場已經睇到係根本擺明唔踢<br />\n<br />\n一日未傾掂一日都渣流灘"},{"pid":"f15c49a3c437131203c341836af6dd192957e60b","tid":1123834,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"我屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦 bill哥"},{"pid":"d89bba73a9556b9dbb28a00ed2d8a7e7fcb64412","tid":1123834,"uid":68319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"Ten percent luck<br />\nTwenty percent skill<br />\nFifteen percent 大佬彪<br />\nFive percent pleasure<br />\nFifty percent pain"},{"pid":"8c259fdc20ad08e910086b25d1e0471241a9fbec","tid":1123834,"uid":120965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"屌你 買左曼聯架仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bea445da4842d42e4ba2a2b983b469b5ef77d96","tid":1123834,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"打咁大段野燈"},{"pid":"e0f2b669b7df7eeb3cf4f2528aa6bc460247a8e6","tid":1123834,"uid":203542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"夜啦 收皮啦 打少d飛機啦49000"},{"pid":"27e47fc319e9015444be5baafc5fe3de2c2e58bb","tid":1123834,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:54:06.000Z","msg":"本身想買獌<br />\n等緊正選名單<br />\n彪哥出手而家慳返"},{"pid":"d6ed54d99e1dfa31d21baf70210837a0eebc1233","tid":1123834,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"多謝all in 對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023b22ebe2fb2e43911bf18f8d174ada18ed1a67","tid":1123834,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"有彪哥加持 可重注曼"},{"pid":"e1baaf02bff7ee68240fdc4c3235b1d361588abd","tid":1123834,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89bba73a9556b9dbb28a00ed2d8a7e7fcb64412","tid":1123834,"uid":68319,"like":5,"disli